column2: mneaiaak𑄴ksa+mr𑄴 bek𑄴unor𑄴 man𑄳raakgoc𑄴

yaaiyyaanat𑄳yyaae mneai girir𑄴 bek𑄴unat𑄳yyaa𑄴 sa+m aao ttnttn𑄳yyaa𑄴 bnbn𑄳yyaa𑄴 aak𑄴ks+maanii aa𑄳aa aamana jdar𑄴 aaic𑄴jodar𑄴 mnnii halad𑄳yyaae pitiimit𑄴 sn𑄴di, sdhiinat aa𑄳aa gam𑄴 bijherar𑄴 khudhi aaibe;

yaaiyyaanat𑄳yyaae mneai aak𑄴ks+maaar𑄴 p𑄳rati aaalehan𑄴 aa𑄳aa ghinenr𑄴 phale mneaihor𑄴 aaed lc𑄴kheneai aaedok𑄳yyaa𑄴 gari aaemn𑄴 mrn dok𑄳yyaa𑄴 bedhok𑄳yyaa𑄴 km𑄴 garineai aa𑄳aa yaaiyyaanat𑄳yyaae aaedok𑄳yyaa𑄴 aaek𑄳h𑄴n𑄴 pitiimir𑄴 phuriuudineai aaajaaac𑄴 mneaihor𑄴 bega ddngar𑄴 aajh gar hayyaae, yaaiyyaanat𑄴 bek𑄴 mneaihor𑄴 dhar𑄴ma aa𑄳aa kadh kanr𑄴 ju pebk𑄴 aa𑄳aa kana rt𑄴 aao na ddoreyyaae ji+mknii kdebk𑄴;

yaaiyyaanat𑄳yyaae mneai yaa𑄳yyaaen𑄴 kl𑄴kd aao mer𑄴pdho m𑄱yyaat𑄴 begathumor𑄴 ju aaijhebe lreai gat𑄳yyaa𑄴 tidebaar𑄴 n𑄳ha han𑄴 senat𑄳yyaa𑄴 aaaainor𑄴 ssan𑄴 dineai mneaiyyaaor𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m thup𑄴 garn bega ddngar𑄴 garac;
yaaiyyaanat𑄳yyaae jdar𑄴 mat𑄴dh𑄳yyaaa ghnt𑄳yyaae jhk𑄴gari doledleai samre thnr𑄴 jugol𑄴 khmkaiai garn;

yaaiyyaanat𑄳yyaae sadas𑄳yyaaa jt𑄴un𑄴 jtisa+mghar𑄴 sanade aar+m mneaiyyaaor𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m, mneai keyyaaer𑄴 aaic𑄴jot𑄴 aao dm𑄴 aa𑄳aa mile maradar𑄴 sa+m aak𑄴ks+maaar𑄴 p𑄳rati trr𑄴 bic𑄴sec𑄴 tuli dhareneai aa𑄳aa aa𑄳ham sdhiinatr𑄴 cglt𑄴 smjik𑄴 uujonii aa𑄳aa ji+mknii calnr𑄴 uujoniir𑄴 mn𑄴 aagebt𑄳yyaa𑄴 daramara hoyyaaon𑄴;

yaaiyyaanat𑄳yyaae sadas𑄳yyaaa rej𑄳yyaaayyaani jtisa+mghar𑄴 balbal𑄴diyyaaeai mneaiaak𑄴ks+m aao aar+m sdhiinataaniir𑄴 p𑄳rati bek𑄴unat𑄳yyaa𑄴 aaic𑄴jot𑄴 brn aa𑄳aa aaedrr𑄴 damedle khmkaiai plnr𑄴 tk𑄴gari phebt𑄳yyaae aaimn𑄴-jabn𑄴 aaek𑄴jadh;
yaaiyyaanat𑄳yyaae aae sdhiinat aa𑄳aa aak𑄴ks+maanii aaek𑄳h𑄴n𑄴 aaajeaaac𑄴 tter𑄴pn aae aaimn𑄴-jamn𑄴 puro garibt𑄳yyaa𑄴 bega ddngar𑄴 km𑄴

mneaiaak𑄴ksa+mr𑄴 bek𑄴unor𑄴 man𑄳raakgoc𑄴
leghi niyyaaom𑄴 bneyyaaon𑄴

aae ddik𑄴lresan𑄴 bek𑄴 jti aa𑄳aa rej𑄳yyaaar𑄴 gam𑄴phalar𑄴 aaajeaaac𑄴 aaek𑄳h𑄴n𑄴 khudho aaijhebhe km𑄴 gari yaaeba, yaaiyyaanat𑄴 aaikaa𑄱 aaikaa𑄱 mnuc𑄴 aa𑄳aa samjar𑄴 aaikaa𑄱 aaikaa𑄱 herdom aae ddik𑄴lresannare nitaa𑄱 aaidot𑄴 tuli parisunan aao sighenloi𑄱 aaeai sdhiinat aao aak𑄴ks+maaniir𑄴 p𑄳rati s𑄳rat𑄴dh jgebr𑄴 ceret𑄳h𑄴 garibhe aa𑄳aa bek𑄴 sadas𑄳yyaaa rej𑄳yyaaa aao trr𑄴 dakhalii bhiidheuuunot𑄴 jt𑄴unor𑄴 aaudhouuut𑄳yyaae jtiiyyaaa aao god pitiimit𑄴 ceret𑄳h𑄴r𑄴 mt𑄴dhame aaeai aak𑄴ks+m aa𑄳aa sdhiinataanii bek𑄴unor𑄴 aao gunot𑄴 lghe  pr km𑄴 garilan aa𑄳aa se kmn𑄴 gamedleai pln𑅁
dhr 1
bek𑄴 mnuc𑄴 niribhili sa+m aaic𑄴jot𑄴 aa𑄳aa aak𑄴ks+m nineai jan𑄴mn𑄴𑅁 trr𑄴 aaed aa𑄳aa but𑄴dhi aaghe; senat𑄳yyaa𑄴 bek𑄴unar𑄴 aaek𑄴jan𑄴 aarek𑄴 janar𑄴 p𑄳rati gam𑄴 dol𑄴 cid𑄳yyaae nineai caln uucit𑄴𑅁
dhr 2

aae leghi kayyaae degeyyaae sdhiinat aa𑄳aa aak𑄴ksa+mr𑄴 gutii, dhar𑄴ma, bar𑄴na, sik𑄴kh, bhc𑄴, rjanitik𑄴 b nnk𑄳h𑄴n𑄴 mat𑄴, jtiiyyaa𑄴 b smjik𑄴 phuriuut𑄳yyaa𑄴, jan𑄴ma, sam𑄴patii b aaan𑄳yyaaa kana aaic𑄴jot𑄴 bc𑄴bijer𑄴 chr bek𑄴une sa+m aak𑄴ks+m theba𑅁

kana dec𑄴 ba mdibhider𑄴 rjanitik𑄴, simine b pitiimir𑄴 aaic𑄴joda uuugure tr𑄴 kana aaadhibsiir𑄴 p𑄳rati kanaragam𑄴 terac𑄴 merac𑄴 gar na haba; se dec𑄴 b mdibhide sdhiin𑄴 hok𑄴, hok𑄴 aaachibhukaa, aaasyyaaitaassita ki+mb sr𑄴babhaumataar𑄴 aaan𑄳yyaaa kana siminer𑄴 bhidire𑅁
dhr 3
ji+mkni, sdhiinat aa𑄳aa keyyaae rak𑄴khet𑄳yyaa𑄴 bek𑄴unor𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m aaghe𑅁
dhr 4
krare aamanatale b kmat𑄳yyaa𑄴 bn𑄳hi rgh yaaeda nayyaa𑄴𑅁 bek𑄴 dharanar𑄴 km𑄴kdeyyaae aa𑄳aa gbur𑄴gareyyaae bepr𑄴 bhac𑄴 neyaa haba𑅁
dhr 5
krare mr𑄴pit𑄴 gar na yaaeba; ki+mb krar𑄴 p𑄳rati aadnii, aaamneaiyyaaor𑄴 b aaagamnar𑄴 kadhbt𑄳h𑄴 k𑄳ha na yaaeba aa𑄳aa krare aaedok𑄳yyaa𑄴 sc𑄴ti diyyaa na yaaeba𑅁
dhr 6
aaaainor𑄴 muju+myyaae bek𑄴un𑄴 mnuc𑄴 aaiyaaebhe aaijhep𑄴 hobhr𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m aaghe𑅁
dhr 7

aaaainor𑄴 cogot𑄴 bek𑄴une sa+m aa𑄳aa bek𑄴 mnuc𑄴 sabur𑄳ha𑄱𑄱 bek𑄴une aaaainor𑄴 aac𑄴s𑄳rayyaa𑄴 sa+mgari phebk𑄴𑅁 aaeai leghi kayyaae kadhghn𑄴 na mni aaemen𑄴 kana uuno b duno phragar𑄴 km𑄴 gari sa+m gari aac𑄴s𑄳rayyaa𑄴 lbhar𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m bek𑄴unar𑄴 aaghe𑅁
dhr 8
ssan𑄴tat𑄳re b aaaaine diyyaa aar+m aak𑄴ks+m na mnile sak𑄳yyaa𑄴 yaaadebade jtiiyyaa𑄴 bijer𑄴 aadladat𑄴un𑄴 gam𑄴 dol𑄴 km𑄴 phebt𑄳yyaa𑄴 bek𑄴unar𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m rayyaae𑅁
dhr 9
krare yaaak𑄳yyaa𑄴sak𑄳yyaa𑄴 bni nejn b bniithan ki+mb rej𑄳yyaaa chr gar na yaaeba𑅁
dhr 10

aamanar𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m aao km𑄴 knt𑄴 tuliden aa𑄳aa aamanar𑄴 mane na kaneai aan𑄳yyaa𑄴 phaujadri nlic𑄴 mbibet𑄳yyaa𑄴 bek𑄴unor𑄴 puro sa+m gari aaek𑄳h𑄴n𑄴 sdhiin𑄴 aa𑄳aa nirapek𑄴kha bijer𑄴-aadladat𑄴 p𑄳raks𑄳yyaaa sunni sebr𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m rayyaae𑅁
dhr 11
sc𑄴tidibr𑄴 aaabardhe dujii hale bek𑄴 mnujor𑄴 aamanapakaa bal𑄴den khmkaiai aak𑄴ks+mhayyaae aaek𑄳h𑄴n𑄴 p𑄳raks𑄳yyaaa aadladat𑄴 aaaain𑄴aaanusre duc𑄴 dhuri na phn sa+m nir𑄴duc𑄴 kanr𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m theba𑅁

krare aaedok𑄳yyaa𑄴 kana km𑄴 b bhulot𑄳yyaa𑄴 sc𑄴tir𑄴 aaabardhe dujii k𑄳ha na yaaeba, yaae km𑄴 b bhul𑄴 hanr𑄴 samayyaa𑄴 jtiiyyaaa b pitiimir𑄴 aaaaine dan𑄴ddaniiyyaa𑄴 aaabart𑄴 na aaela𑅁 sc𑄴tidiber𑄴 aaabart𑄴 hanr𑄴 samayyaa𑄴 yaae sc𑄴ti phebr𑄴 aaela, tt𑄴un𑄴 bajamn𑄴 ddngar𑄴 sc𑄴ti diyyaa na yaaeba𑅁
dhr 12

kra nijor𑄴 gopan𑄴 ki+mb tr𑄴 gharar𑄴, giri aao cidhipdir𑄴 aaic𑄳yyaa𑄴mata jiyyaan𑄴pai garn ki+mb tr𑄴 sunm𑄴 aao  aaic𑄴joda uurure pire phude pr gar na caliba𑅁 aae bbat𑄳yyaa𑄴 jiyyaan𑄴pai garn b pirepnr𑄴 pic𑄴siyyaan𑄴di aaaainor𑄴 aac𑄴s𑄳rayyaa𑄴 lbhar𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m bek𑄴unor𑄴 rayyaae𑅁
dhr 13
aamanar𑄴 rej𑄳yyaaar𑄴 cerahit𑄳yyaa𑄴di sdhin𑄴bhbe larcar aa𑄳aa thebt𑄳yyaa𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m bek𑄴unor𑄴 rayyaae𑅁
bek𑄴unor𑄴 aamanar𑄴 dec𑄴sumut𑄴do yaae kana dec𑄴 chrijn aa𑄳aa aamanadejat𑄴 phiri aaejnr𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m rayyaae𑅁
dhr 14
mr𑄴pidot𑄴un𑄴 rak𑄴khe pebt𑄳yyaa𑄴 nnk𑄳h𑄴n𑄴 dejat𑄴 aas𑄳rayyaa𑄴 p𑄳rr𑄴than garn aa𑄳aa se dejar𑄴 aas𑄳rayyaae thnr𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m bek𑄴unar𑄴 rayyaae𑅁
aaarjanitik𑄴 aaabart𑄴 aa𑄳aa jtisa+mghar𑄴 uudic𑄳yyaae aa𑄳aa muul𑄴niitir𑄴 bengkang kmat𑄴un𑄴 gec𑄴siyyaak𑄴gari phuri uut𑄳yyaa𑄴 nlijor𑄴 lage aae aak𑄴ks+m p𑄳rr𑄴than na garn yaaeai pre𑅁
dhr 15
bek𑄴unor𑄴 aaek𑄳h𑄴n𑄴 jtiiyyaaatr𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m rayyaae𑅁
krare yaaak𑄳yyaa𑄴sak𑄳yyaa𑄴 jiyyaan𑄴 manehayyaa𑄴 tr𑄴 jtiiyyaaatt𑄴un𑄴 bhk𑄴 nadent𑄴un𑄴 bt𑄴 diyyaa na yaaeba, ki+mb kra jtiiyyaaat lrebr𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m bt𑄴 diyyaa na yaaeba𑅁
dhr 16
dhar𑄴ma, gutii aao jti bek𑄴une buro bayyaaajar𑄴 marat𑄴miler𑄴 mel gar aa𑄳aa giri bnebr𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m rayyaae𑅁 mel, negamogor𑄴jii+mknii aa𑄳aa nek𑄴mok𑄴 srsri d𑄳yyaaedi trr𑄴 sa+m aak𑄴ks+m theba𑅁
melt𑄴 mun𑄴juk𑄴 marat𑄴miler𑄴 sdhiin𑄴 aa𑄳aa puro aa𑄳hi puran hal𑄳he t𑄳yyaae mel km𑄴 thum𑄴 haba𑅁
giri halad𑄳yyaae samjar𑄴 aaajeaaac𑄴 aa𑄳aa aar+m gutii-aaekak𑄴, senat𑄳yyaae samc𑄴 aao rej𑄳yyaaat𑄴un𑄴 nirpat𑄳h𑄴 lbhar𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m rayyaae𑅁
dhr 17
bek𑄴unar𑄴 gai aa𑄳aa aaan𑄳yyaaajanar𑄴 samre milineai mili sam𑄴patiir𑄴 mlik𑄴 habr𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m aaghe𑅁
krare yaaak𑄳yyaa𑄴sak𑄳yyaa𑄴 jingiri singiri tr𑄴 sam𑄴patiiun𑄴 bt𑄴 diyyaa na yaaeba𑅁
dhr 18

bek𑄴unar𑄴 dhar𑄴ma, aaed aao cid𑄳yyaae sdhiinatyyaa𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m rayyaae𑅁 aae aak𑄴ks+m samre dhar𑄴ma b bic𑄴sec𑄴 badalnr𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m aa𑄳aa aaeai samre, degepr b mure mure, gai b aaan𑄳yyaaar𑄴 samre milineai, sik𑄴khedn𑄴, lr𑄴cr𑄴, dhiyyaan𑄴 garn b plebr𑄴 mt𑄴dhame dhar𑄴ma b bic𑄴sec𑄴 garibr𑄴 aak𑄴ks+maao aaiyyaaot𑄴 theba𑅁
dhr 19

bek𑄴unar𑄴 mat𑄴 dibr𑄴 aa𑄳aa mat𑄴 phagad+mngir𑄴 sdhiinatyyaa𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m rayyaae𑅁 aaagur𑄴 mat𑄴 didr𑄴 aa𑄳aa rej𑄳yyaaar𑄴 simine cauhitii yaae kana mt𑄴dhame khabar𑄴 pn dok𑄳yyaa𑄴 aa𑄳aa tataa𑄱 gepan𑄴, lan aao aaudholan sdhiinataao aae aak𑄴ks+maaar𑄴 mat𑄴dh𑄳yyaa pare𑅁
dhr 20
bek𑄴unar𑄴 sn𑄴tipunaa𑄱 khalt𑄴 aaejn aao samiti garnr𑄴 sdhiinatyyaa𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m rayyaae𑅁
krare kana jadhjat𑄳yyaa𑄴 hant𑄴 bale jor𑄴 gar yaaeda nayyaa𑄴𑅁
dhr 21
nije nije b aaabhedar𑄴 bjilan mnuc𑄴janar𑄴 mt𑄴dhame aamana dejar𑄴 ssan𑄴 pariclanyyaa𑄴 aaa+msag𑄳rahan𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m bek𑄴unar𑄴 rayyaae𑅁
aamanar𑄴 dejar𑄴 sar𑄴krii cguriit𑄴 sa+m ju phebr𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m bek𑄴unar𑄴 rayyaae𑅁

janagannar𑄴 mun𑄴juk𑄴 haboi sar𑄴krar𑄴 ssan𑄴 khematr𑄴 khudho; aaeai mun𑄴juk𑄴 din𑄴mgene aaak𑄴ta mujime gec𑄴siyyaak𑄴 nir𑄴bcanar𑄴 mt𑄴dhame haba; aar𑄴 b𑄳yyaalat𑄴 ki+mb sa+m sa+myyaae kana aaabhedar𑄴 bhot𑄴 denr𑄴 niyyaaame aaiyyaan𑄴 haba𑅁
dhr 22

samjar𑄴 sadas𑄳yyaaa aaijhebe bek𑄴unar𑄴 smjik𑄴 nirpat𑄳h𑄴r𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m aaghe𑅁 jtiiyyaaa ceret𑄳h𑄴 aao pitiimir𑄴 bal𑄴diyyaadir𑄴 mt𑄴dhame roj𑄳yyaaar𑄴 sa+mjadh aao sam𑄴padar𑄴 samre samn𑄴 rgeneai bek𑄴unare aamanar𑄴 aaicjot𑄴 aa𑄳aa mnar𑄴 aaabhedar𑄴 phagadngat𑄳yyaae khmkaiai smjik𑄴, aaar𑄴thanitik𑄴 aao s+mc𑄴k𑄳ritik𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m aadyyaaar𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m rayyaae𑅁
dhr 23
bek𑄴unar𑄴 km𑄴 garibr𑄴, sdhiin𑄴gari cguriilabr𑄴, kmar𑄴 tthik𑄴dm𑄴 aa𑄳aa gam𑄴 paribec𑄴 phebr𑄴 aajhyyaa𑄴 aa𑄳aa km𑄴napnt𑄴un𑄴 muk𑄴ta habr𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m rayyaae𑅁
kanaragam𑄴 bec𑄴kam𑄴 chr sa+m kmat𑄴 sa+m betan𑄴 pnr𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m bek𑄴unar𑄴 aaghe𑅁

km𑄴 garan𑄴 aaedok𑄳yyaae bek𑄴unar𑄴 aamanar𑄴 aa𑄳aa girir𑄴 mnabik𑄴 aaic𑄴jot𑄴 sa+mgac𑄳yyaae khmkaiai bjithebr𑄴 di pre aaidik𑄳yyaae ttik𑄴 aao gam𑄴 pris𑄳ramik𑄴 pebr𑄴 aajhyyaa𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m rayyaae; dak𑄴kr𑄴 majim𑄴 aaiyyaanare nnk𑄳h𑄴n𑄴 smjik𑄴 nirpat𑄳h𑄴 dineai breai diyyaa yaaeai pre𑅁
aamanar𑄴 bhlet𑄴 rghebht𑄳yyaae bek𑄴unar𑄴 tt𑄳ret𑄴 aaiuuniyyaaan𑄴 garn aa𑄳aa siyyaanat𑄴 samibr𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m rayyaae𑅁
dhr 24
bek𑄴unar𑄴 jhiren aao aajher𑄴 thrn𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m rayyaae; din𑄴mgene aaak𑄴ta mujim𑄴 betan𑄴sumut𑄴d𑄳yyaaa chutti aa𑄳aa pesgata kmar𑄴 yaauk𑄴tisa+m siimaao aae aak𑄴ks+m bhidire rayyaae𑅁
dhr 25

khn, chulum𑄴 kbar𑄴, thnr𑄴ghar𑄴, cikit𑄴s𑄳yyaa aao dar𑄴krii samc𑄴 gam𑄴kmniir𑄴 ju aa𑄳aa aae samre pire, laricari nabj𑄳yyaae, lok𑄴dhak𑄳yyaaburo aa𑄳aa jii+mkniit𑄴 khmkaiai ghadibho nnk𑄳h𑄴n𑄴 nabrnr𑄴 lage nirpat𑄳h𑄴 aa𑄳aa bekr𑄴 hale nirpat𑄳h𑄴r𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m sumut𑄴d𑄳yyaaa aamanar𑄴 aa𑄳aa nija girir𑄴 keyyaae aa𑄳aa gamat𑄳yyaa𑄴 aaagur𑄴 jiiban𑄴mnar𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m bek𑄴unar𑄴 rayyaae𑅁

maaabac𑄴th aa𑄳aa sigon𑄴kla aaabac𑄴thyyaa𑄴 aaikaa𑄱 aaikaa𑄱 mile aa𑄳aa sigon𑄴 guror𑄴 game dleai pln aa𑄳aa bal𑄴 pn𑄳h𑄴r𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m aaghe𑅁 mok𑄴lanaaabac𑄴th-bredi ki+mb mok𑄴lanaaabac𑄴thai bek𑄴 gurogun𑄴 lmlm𑄳yyaae nayyaa𑄴 se bbat𑄳yyaae smjik𑄴 nirpat𑄳h𑄴 pebk𑄴𑅁
dhr 26

bek𑄴unar𑄴 sik𑄴khe pebr𑄴 aak𑄴ks+m rayyaae𑅁 na haleaao pat𑄴that𑄴 aao aar+m aaak𑄴taat𑄴 sik𑄴khe bek𑄴unat𑄳yyaae haba𑅁 pat𑄴tham𑄴 sik𑄴khe khmkaiai haba𑅁 krigari aao b𑄳ritiimuulak𑄴 sik𑄴khe aaajeaaac𑄴 aaabac𑄴thai pebr𑄴 ju theba aa𑄳aa aaugurepal𑄳h𑄴 sik𑄴khe b𑄳reaain𑄴 thnr𑄴 aaugure bek𑄴unat𑄳yyaae sa+m gari khulo theba𑅁
